    <title>New: BILL009(26) (Honolulu) — CCL</title>
    <updated>2026-05-30T07:33:27+00:00</updated>
    <link rel="alternate" href="https://hnldoc.ehawaii.gov/hnldoc/measure/3597"/>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RELATING TO FUNDS.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Abolishes the Pauahi Project Expenditures, Hawaii R-15 Fund. Upon its abolishment, the BFS Director shall transfer any remaining moneys to another appropriate fund. Takes effect on July 1, 2026.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Latest action: Passed first reading.&lt;/p&gt;
